OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBright or
OL,6,Fclear spells continue as showers die
OL,7,Fout during this evening. Then becoming
OL,8,Fdry but rain will spread to Dumfries
OL,9,Fand Galloway later on.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,12,Flocally heavy rain during the morning.
OL,13,FBecoming drier in the afternoon with
OL,14,Fjust a few showers.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FOutbreaks
OL,17,Fof locally heavy rain on Friday. Early
OL,18,Fshowers on Saturday then dry. Dry and
OL,19,Fbright on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
